Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.77,0:22:47.86,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}是從哪裡出現的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.89,0:22:51.22,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}這扇前所未有的門
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.28,0:22:52.47,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}醒來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.66,0:22:55.99,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}我還未被人發現的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.20,0:22:58.99,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}因為那一定不是錯覺啊
