Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.84,0:23:12.60,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}已經快要溢出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.64,0:23:15.08,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}但是從伸出的指尖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.14,0:23:17.50,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}傳來的疑惑的訊號
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.54,0:23:20.18,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}這樣的你也很棒哦
